16 WHEREAS, despite his statewide responsibilities, he remained deeply connected to Bartow
17 County, often recognizing local leaders during his speeches and collaborating closely with
18 the Cartersville-Bartow County Chamber of Commerce; and
19 WHEREAS, Bruce Thompson's profound contributions and enduring legacy of service to the
20 Cartersville-Bartow County Chamber of Commerce, Bartow County, and the State of
21 Georgia make him a well-deserved recipient of this prestigious award.
22 NOW, THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED BY THE HOUSE OF REPRESENTATIVES that
23 the members of this body honor the life and legacy of Bruce Thompson upon his posthumous
24 receipt of the Cartersville-Bartow County Chamber of Commerce 2024 Chairman's Award;
25 express their deepest commendation for his efficient, effective, and dedicated public service
26 to the State of Georgia; and extend sincere best wishes to his family for their continued
27 strength and grace.
28 BE IT FURTHER RESOLVED that the Clerk of the House of Representatives is authorized
29 and directed to make an appropriate copy of this resolution available for distribution to the
30 family of Bruce Thompson.
